rows.label: tev041601_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Vio about recent developments.

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ganglion first tried to side with Tree Clan.
Did you know this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0002
rows.name:
They said we could show strength of Prone to universe.
Ha! All talk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0003
rows.name: We refused. Tree Clan will not obey cowards.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0004
rows.name:
Then they allied with Cavern Clan. Nearly destroyed us.
But we regret nothing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0005
rows.name:
Cavern Clan are like bent twigs on ground.
But Tree Clan stand tall. We are stronger! Wiser![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0010
rows.name:
Sajif Scoppio says we need tactics to survive
upcoming battles. He is always lecturing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0011
rows.name: He may end up too smart for his own good. Ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0012
rows.name:
His lectures are too long. I could slay five Cavern Clan
scum before he finished![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0013
rows.name:
Next time he uses mouth, I use fists.
I will prove my tactics are best![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Why did you try to reason with Ganglion?
They do not listen to reason![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0019
rows.name:
If you show weakness? Let your guard down?
That is when they kill all that you love.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0020
rows.name: I hope you heard last battle's message.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0021
rows.name: Next time you see them, pull trigger! No talk![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0026
rows.name:
You go to Cauldros to start big fight? Do not worry.
We will take care of city while you are gone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0027
rows.name:
If Ganglion attacks, we knock them back into space!
Ha ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0028
rows.name: Now hit them with all you have. Do not look back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0033
rows.name:
On my last hunt, I was attacked by Ganglion survivors.
Of course, I made short work of them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0034
rows.name:
Yet it is still worrisome.
Without leader, they have become mad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0035
rows.name:
Some have seen survivors more threatening than any
Ganglion we faced before.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG0036
rows.name:
Be ready if you explore Mira.
Wounded beasts are most dangerous![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG1001
rows.name: Sajif taught me about "strategy."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG1002
rows.name:
I am starting to see appeal.
You Earth aliens think of everything![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG1003
rows.name:
In next battle, I will use "crane's wing" formation to
surprise Ganglion. I will destroy them like bird of prey![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG2001
rows.name:
I have no need of your "strategy," Earth alien.
But I admire your strength.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG2002
rows.name:
You are not all talk like Sajif.
You are true warrior who faces Ganglion unafraid![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG2003
rows.name:
We should hunt together sometime.
Maybe near Janpath Lake?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041601_MSG2004
rows.name:
Worthy prey called Ghuri the Pursuer roams north
shore. Forget strategy. We crush it with bare hands![ST:wait ]
